data.description: Looking for a home with room to spread out and a great spot for morning coffee? Is homesteading your dream? THIS is the place. The home has lots of updates including a beautiful new kitchen and new paint in most rooms. The master has his and hers closets with a large bath and adjoined office that could be used as a nursery if desired. Basement offers two bedrooms, full bath, additional playroom/bedroom, den & large laundry room. A little over 3 mostly flat acres you will find a detached two car garage with heated & cooled bonus space stubbed for bathroom above. The shop offers working space, 9000lb lift and a large open heated/cooled apartment with kitchen & full bath. Need more storage? There is also a large barn with gravel floor. The views from the large back porch are breathtaking. Pond offers small boat launch for boat or kayak. Properties like this do not come available often!
